      "id": "4b3f3088-0cf5-4e45-8977-d61dcabad3c5_787e42bc-17a0-47ca-823e-aed62c88293d",
      "label": "Why are you interested in Mintlify?",
      "type": "textarea",
      "required": true,
      "value": "I'm excited about the opportunity to work at Mintlify because I'm drawn to organizations that operate at scale, solve complex technical challenges, and prioritize innovation and long-term impact. Throughout my experience at Microsoft and Amazon Robotics, I've enjoyed working at the intersection of technology, operations, and strategy — leading cross-functional initiatives, building scalable systems, and driving measurable business outcomes.\n\nWhat particularly interests me about Mintlify is the opportunity to contribute to high-impact products and programs while collaborating with talented teams across engineering, product, and business functions. I'm especially motivated by environments where I can combine technical depth with program leadership to improve reliability, automation, and operational efficiency.\n\nIn my current role, I've led large-scale resilience and automation initiatives, developed AI-driven workflow solutions, and managed complex cross-organizational programs under executive visibility. I enjoy taking ambiguous problems, creating structure, and driving execution from concept through delivery. I'd be excited to bring that same mindset to Mintlify while continuing to grow in a fast-paced and innovative environment.\n\nBeyond the technical challenges, I'm also looking for a company whose culture emphasizes ownership, collaboration, and continuous improvement. From what I've seen, Mintlify aligns strongly with those values, which makes the opportunity especially compelling to me.",
